{"title": "Using Kerberos", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "getting-started/using-kerberos", "html": "<h1 id=\"using-kerberos\">Using Kerberos</h1>\n<h2 id=\"using-kerberos_1\">Using Kerberos</h2>\n<p>NetExec does support Kerberos authentication. There are two options:&#x20;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Using password/hash which automatically takes care of handling the TGT/ST</li>\n<li>Using an existing ticket by specifying the file via the <code>KRB5CCNAME</code> environment variable</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>$<span class=\"w\"> </span>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.0<span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">14393</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:ZORO<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>signing:False<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>SMBv1:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\&lt;</span>username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Or, using <code>--use-kcache</code></p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>$<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/home/user/impacket/administrator.ccache<span class=\"w\"> </span>\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--use-kcache\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.0<span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">14393</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:ZORO<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>signing:False<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>SMBv1:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\a</span>dministrator<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--use-kcache<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>whoami\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.0<span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">14393</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:ZORO<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>signing:False<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>SMBv1:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\a</span>dministrator<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Executed<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">command</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\a</span>dministrator\n\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">export</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KRB5CCNAME</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/home/user/impacket/user.ccache\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--use-kcache<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>whoami\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.0<span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">14393</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:ZORO<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>signing:False<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>SMBv1:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nSMB<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\">    </span>ZORO<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\&lt;</span>username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Example with LDAP and option <code>--kdcHost</code></p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ldap<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>--kdcHost<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nSMB<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">445</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>DC01<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>.0<span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>x64<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:DC01<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>signing:True<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>SMBv1:False<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>\nLDAP<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">389</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>DC01<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Using Kerberos Using Kerberos NetExec does support Kerberos authentication. There are two options:&#x20; Using password/hash which automatically takes care of handling the TGT/ST Using an existing ticket by specifying the file via the KRB5CCNAME…", "tags": []}